      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOBLE TOBY (2) impressed last time when produced a slick 21.93 win here in a new PB this course and distance. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest. EASTLY BREEZE (1) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten half a length (16.75) behind She's A Kiwi at Q Straight. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to be in this for a long way. SHIMMERING LIGHT (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Q Parklands in a handy 30.36 beating Majestic Zeal. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expecting another bold showing. HOPE MOO MOO (6) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
